analysis.title: Global Market Outlook
analysis.content: Neutral regime persists as volatility expands. The OmniMetric GMS at 52 validates a transition into a cautious expansionary phase where liquidity convexity is challenged by a VIX ascent above 20. While credit spread compression in the high-yield sector suggests resilient solvency, the stagnant net liquidity and flat OGV vector signal a loss of cyclical momentum. Risk-off sentiment is emerging through regime degradation in equity indices, though AI-driven sector rotations provide a synthetic floor. [ACTION: WAIT FOR PULLBACK]

Risk-off sentiment is emerging through regime degradation in equity indices, though AI-driven sector rotations provide a synthetic floor. [ACTION: WAIT FOR PULLBACK]

Meskipun kompresi spread kredit menunjukkan solvabilitas yang tangguh, likuiditas neto yang stagnan dan vektor OGV yang datar menandakan hilangnya momentum siklis. Sentimen risk-off muncul melalui degradasi rezim pada indeks ekuitas, meskipun rotasi sektor yang didorong oleh AI memberikan bantalan sintetis. [ACTION: WAIT FOR PULLBACK]

reports.DE: Neutrales Regime besteht bei steigender Volatilitt. Der GMS von 52 besttigt den bergang in eine vorsichtige Expansionsphase, in der die Liquidittskonvexitt durch einen VIX ber 20 herausgefordert wird. Whrend die Kompression der Kreditspreads auf Resilienz hindeutet, signalisieren stagnierende Nettoliquiditt und ein flacher OGV-Vektor den Verlust zyklischer Dynamik. Risk-Off-Sentiment entsteht durch Regimedegradation in Aktienindizes, wobei KI-getriebene Sektorrotationen einen Boden bilden. [ACTION: WAIT FOR PULLBACK]
